    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People or beings famed for rescuing others from danger, harm, or difficulty; in religious contexts, particularly Christian, refers to a deity offering salvation to mankind and redemption from sin.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
